tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DiseaseOutbreakPredictions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  environmental_factor VARCHAR(255),
  population_health_data VARCHAR(255),
  outbreak_prediction VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE DiseaseOutbreaks (
    outbreak_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    outbreak_date DATE,
    disease_name VARCHAR(100),
    reported_cases INT
);

CREATE TABLE EnvironmentalFactors (
    factor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    factor_type VARCHAR(100),
    factor_value FLOAT,
    recorded_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE DiseaseCases (
    case_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    disease_name VARCHAR(255),
    num_cases INT
)

CREATE TABLE EnvironmentalFactors (
    factor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE PopulationHealth (
    health_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    population_size INT,
    health_condition VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE PredictiveModels (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    trained_date DATE,
    accuracy FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE DiseaseCases ( 
	id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
	date DATE, 
	location TEXT, 
	disease_name TEXT, 
	number_of_cases INT 
)

CREATE TABLE EnvironmentalFactors ( 
	id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
	date DATE, 
	location TEXT, 
	temperature FLOAT, 
	humidity FLOAT 
)

CREATE TABLE PopulationHealthData ( 
	id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
	location TEXT, 
	population_size INT,

	model_name TEXT,
